</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/TheAdventuresOfGynoStar" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/TheAdventuresOfGynoStar">The Adventures of Gyno-Star</a></em>: Supervillain Vlad Deferens tries to use a shock collar to make Gyno-Star compliant and obedient.
